MCA Inc said noted filmmaker Steven Spielberg will serve as creative consultant forUniversal Studios Tour Florida.    The tour is a joint venture between MCA and Cineplex OdeonCorp that is scheduled to open in 1989.    MCA is also planning a major expansion of its UniversalStudio Tours. The expansion includes four live-action showsbased films and TV series, including Spielberg's "E.T.".    MCA's actions are seen as spurred by The Disney Co's &lt;DIS>Chairman Michal Eisner's intention to build a new attraction inthe Los Angeles area, possibly a studio tour. Reuter&#3;